description:
What happens when God takes decisive action? One instance is when God chose to end violence among the antediluvians, those who lived before the flood. Discover God's active role in preserving humanity by choosing Noah's family as a remnant to start anew. Discover the importance of recognizing God's hatred for evil and His commitment to decisive intervention.
